{"tid":825013,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"點解升完WIN 10之後會突然爆C drive","createTime":"2018-09-17T10:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T11:54:25.000Z","uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"937418134fb3db62b830f30613f549578a695267","tid":825013,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T10:26:42.000Z","msg":"原本個C drive都仲有40-50 GB (本身係128GB)<br />\n但係有時會突然之間冇哂 彈個ALERT話我聽個C drive冇位<br />\n我即刻睇下個C drive容量 發現佢上上落落咁<br />\n係咁係KB同MB之間徘徊 甚至去到1byte都冇 轉個頭又多返幾MB 又落返去KB<br />\ncheck過c drive入面既file 都係scan到50 GB左右<br />\n究竟係咩事?? 點解一下會食成幾十GB仲要係咁有file 加加減減??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d15ddc47a7176c22625c90ed74073630a940d3","tid":825013,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"查到好似係windows/temp<br />\n入面有個tmp00000595 gen左幾十GB檔案出黎<br />\n究竟咩事??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00df4f644a87825a9b53c46b11ae65db7017ad6","tid":825013,"uid":78464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"佢會將你舊system back up. 等你隨時可以restore<br />\n如果無無需要<br />\n去返C drive, right click, 清理system 嘅垃圾就得"}]}